{"tid":460631,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(俾番Marvel)傳Fox擬出售大部分業務予迪士尼","createTime":"2017-11-06T23:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T15:57:41.000Z","uid":41343,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"8475d1019211aaad5b0990145242df1bc73ad5c7","tid":460631,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:26:13.000Z","msg":"有報道指, 廿一世紀霍士計劃將新聞和體育以外的業務, 悉數售予和路迪士尼.<br />\n        CNBC引述消息報道, 霍士和迪士尼的交易談判從幾個星期前開始, 但據報談判目前已經停止, 未來可能會繼續. 如果雙方落實交易, 迪士尼將購入霍士的電影製片廠, 電視製作, 以及FX和國家地理網絡, 及其國際資產B Sky B和Star. 但霍士會保留其廣播網絡和體育業務, 因為迪士尼目前已經有ESPN, 若擁有兩個廣播網絡, 可能會被質疑壟斷.<br />\n        消息傳出後, 廿一世紀霍士股價急升超過百分之7, 迪士尼亦升百分之1.6.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsID=20171107034859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20171107034859&d=XK10PQmd2BBqMv3UuF7e3S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5921e42f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsID=20171107034859</a>"},{"pid":"7997bf35e0c95c4b9dc2f121480ea1951304d257","tid":460631,"uid":10608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:28:53.000Z","msg":"Mutants<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ed1e449d8a44dafa6c99e7193d3b5ca0239b3a","tid":460631,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:30:49.000Z","msg":"x man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7763e69bf7899db482bb55061a73cf32bea4afe6","tid":460631,"uid":60357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:32:36.000Z","msg":"成日買起咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1917a19499fd9f7073f5a1dda1bc85366f47a78","tid":460631,"uid":861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:34:13.000Z","msg":"終於肯比返marvel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"